main event: A civilian employee at Kelly AFB observed a cigar-shaped object that flashed low across the sky emitting green, phosphorescent colors.
interesting points: The object was estimated to be flying at a speed of 500 to 600 mph,The sighting lasted for approximately 10 to 15 minutes,No sound was reported except for a faint whistle or exhaust noise,The object was observed at an altitude between 2000 to 7000 feet,There were two confirmed witnesses to the sighting.
